18
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,760
<i>Love.</i>

19
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:20,200
<i>When it's strong,
it makes you jump over the moon.</i>

20
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,560
<i>After breaking up,</i>

21
