<i>it hurts you deeply.</i>

22
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,720
<i>In order to keep our remaining dignity,</i>

23
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:33,120
<i>we must pretend not to care</i>

24
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,640
<i>and be the bigger person.</i>

25
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,880
<i>Pretend that</i>

26
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,400
